<p>
<span class="docSource"><span class="dType"><abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ recipients copy (A recipients copy is assumed to be in the hand of the signer unless it is otherwise described.) ]">RC</abbr></span> (<span class="ref-terms">Adams Papers</span>); endorsed: Mr Dumas Feb. 23. 1782. relative to an House, at the Hague.</span>
</p>
</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA12d187n1-ptr" id="PJA12d187n1">1</a>
<p>The notarized contract, dated 22 Feb. and signed by Dumas as <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr>s agent and the Comtesse de Quadt Wykeradt as the seller, is at Gemeente-Archief, The Hague.</p>
</div>
